Package: proteomicAge
Type: Package
Title: Proteomic Aging Clocks
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-06-18
Authors@R: c(
    person("Xiaohan", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "xiaohan@clawbio.org")
  )
Description: Compute biological age from plasma proteomic data using
    published proteomic aging clocks. Currently implements proteomic
    age models from Tanaka et al. (2018), Lehallier et al. (2019),
    Sathyan et al. (2020), Oh et al. (2023), and Wang et al. (2024).
    All computation is local; proteomic data never leaves the machine.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/EnricMartin/proteomicAge
